## üìå Suggested Practice Order

1. Meeting Rooms I
2. Meeting Rooms II
3. Minimum Platforms
4. Merge Intervals
5. Insert Interval
6. Non-overlapping Intervals
7. Min Arrows to Burst Balloons
8. Car Pooling
9. My Calendar I / II
10. Employee Free Time
11. Skyline Problem (optional advanced)

